<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Création d’un nouveau compte</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f2f6fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .header {
      background: #0f1b28;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header img {
      max-height: 80px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 12px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 25px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0f1b28;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      max-width: 300px;
      width: 80%;
      text-align: center;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        white-space: normal !important;
      }

      .button {
        width: 100% !important;
        max-width: none !important;
        padding: 14px 0 !important;
        font-size: 17px !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="header">
      {% if entite is defined and entite.logo %}
        <img class="logo" src="{{ absolute_url(asset('uploads/photos/entite/logo/' ~ entite.logo)) }}" alt="Logo {{ entite.nom }}">
      {% endif %}
      <h2>Création d’un nouveau compte :<br> <strong>{{ adherent.prenom }}&nbsp;{{ adherent.nom }}</strong></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Bonjour,</p>
      <p>Un nouveau compte vient d’être créé sur la plateforme <strong>Wiki Formation</strong>.</p>
      <p>Adresse e-mail du compte :<br><b>{{ adherent.email }}</b></p>

      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="https://wikiformation.fr" class="button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">🔍 Accéder à la plateforme</a>
      </div>

      <p>Merci de votre confiance,<br>L’équipe <b>Wiki Formation</b></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Wiki Formation<br>
      <a href="https://wikiformation.fr">wikiformation.fr</a> — contact@wikiformation.fr</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>



